videoSnippet.title: Ganguly Style || Yangyi Yu vs Ganguly || FIDE World Team Championship (2019)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Yangyi Yu vs Surya Shekhar Ganguly
FIDE World Team Championship (2019), rd 4, Mar-8
Queen's Gambit Declined: Ragozin Defense (D38)

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Nf3 d5 5. cxd5 exd5 6. Qa4+ Nc6 7. Bg5 h6 8. Bxf6 Qxf6 9. e3 O-O 10. Be2 Be6 11. O-O a6 12. Rfc1 Bd6 13. Qd1 Ne7 14. Na4 b6 15. b4 a5 16. b5 g5 17. Nb2 Ng6 18. Nd3 Rae8 19. Nfe1 h5 20. Bxh5 Kg7 21. h3 Rh8 22. Bg4 Bxg4 23. hxg4 Rxe3 24. Rc6 Bh2+ 25. Kf1 Bg3 26. Kg1 Bh2+ 27. Kf1 Bg3 28. Kg1 Qxd4 29. Nc2 Bh2+ 30. Kh1 Bf4+ 31. Kg1 Bh2+ 32. Kh1 Bf4+ 33. Kg1 Qxd3 34. Nxe3 Bh2+ 35. Kh1 Be5+ 36. Kg1 Bh2+ 37. Kh1 Qxb5 38. Rac1 Bg3+ 39. Kg1 Bh2+ 40. Kh1 Ne7 41. g3 Nxc6 42. Nf5+ Kf8 43. Kg2 Bxg3 44. Nxg3 Rh6 45. Nf5 Re6 46. Qf3 Qb2 47. Rh1 Ne7 48. Qg3 Nxf5 49. gxf5 Re2 50. Qf3 Qe5 51. f6 Ke8 52. Rh8+ Kd7 53. Rf8 Qe6 54. Qh5 Qe4+ 55. Qf3 Qxf3+ 56. Kxf3 Rxa2 57. Rxf7+ Ke6 58. Rxc7 Kxf6 59. Rc6+ Kf5 60. Rxb6 Ra3+ 61. Ke2 a4 62. Rd6 Ke4 63. Re6+ Kd4 64. Rg6 Ra2+ 65. Kf3 a3 66. Rxg5 Rc2

To those of you who read the description: You are an excellent subscriber! :)

The FIDE World Team Championship is a biennial 10-team round-robin tournament that in 2019 is taking place from 5-14 March in Astana, Kazakhstan. Matches take place on four boards, with 2 match points for a win and 1 for a draw. Sweden replaced Poland, who declined their invitation.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, with a 30-second increment starting from move one. No draw offers are allowed until after move 30. Official website: wteams.astana2019.fide.com
